Helper class to generate headers for copying an object from a source to another bucket + key. Construct that holds copy source related data.
param:
source bucket name of source
param:
metadataDirective directive : COPY | REPLACE, default is COPY
param:
otherHeaders other headers such as ETag and Time specifications
